text: Her is geleafa, and gebed, and bletsung, læwedum mannum, ðe ðæt leden ne cunnon.
Ðu ure Fæder, þe eart on heofenum, sy ðin nama gehalgod.
Sy ðin willa swa swa on heofenum swa eac on eorðan.
Syle us todæg urne dæghwomlican hlaf, and forgif us ure gyltas swa swa we forgyfað þam ðe wið us agyltað.
And ne læd þu na us on costnunge, ac alys us fram yfele.
